## 7. systemd unit для `sql_exporter`

Создай `/etc/systemd/system/sql_exporter.service`

```ini
[Unit]
Description=SQL Exporter for Prometheus
After=network-online.target
Wants=network-online.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=sql_exporter
Group=sql_exporter
ExecStart=/opt/sql_exporter/sql_exporter \
  -config.file=/etc/sql_exporter/sql_exporter.yml \
  -web.listen-address=127.0.0.1:9399
Restart=always
RestartSec=5
NoNewPrivileges=true
ProtectSystem=full
ProtectHome=true
PrivateTmp=true
LimitNOFILE=65536
WorkingDirectory=/var/lib/sql_exporter

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

Применение:

```bash
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl enable --now sql_exporter
sudo systemctl status sql_exporter --no-pager
```

Проверка:

```bash
curl -s http://127.0.0.1:9399/metrics | grep '^pgss_db_'
```

Если метрики видны — exporter работает корректно.

